                     <interp inst="t18770305-318-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18770305-318-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp> unlawfully conspiring, together with <persName id="t18770305-name-352">
                        <interp inst="t18770305-name-352" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18770305-name-352" type="surname" value="FRANCIS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18770305-name-352" type="given" value="na"></interp>J. W. Francis</persName> and others, to obtain and obtaining goods from divers persons on false pretences;</rs> Cohen was <hi rend="italic">also</hi> charged with <rs id="t18770305-318-offence-2" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18770305-318-offence-2" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18770305-318-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>receiving the said goods knowing them to have been fraudu<lb></lb>lently obtained.</rs>
